  "marketplace_integration_app_dec_office_preview": "<p>Seamless online preview of office files in Vigor Table, allowing you to view common office files such as Excel, Word, PPT, etc. on your PC or cell phone anywhere, anytime</p\n\n<ul><li>Online preview of .doc, .docx, .xls, .xlsx, .ppt, .pptx, and .pdf formatted office files</li><li>Desktop and mobile simultaneous support for file preview of the above formats\n</li></ul>\n\n<p>Additional notes:</p\n<ul><li>This feature is powered by \"Yoncentric Cloud Conversion\" and officially integrated by Vigilometer</li><li>Click the \"Authorize\" button below to enable this app and agree that \"Yoncentric Cloud Conversion\" reads the office files you want to preview</li><li>If you no longer need the office preview feature, the administrator can visit this page again to disable it</li></ul>",
